query:
with home_homies AS (select *
                     from UNNEST($1::integer[]) as homie_id)
insert
into recent_restaurants (homie_id, user_id, restaurant_id)
select h.id,
       $2,
       r.id
from home_homies hh
         join homies h on h.id = hh.homie_id
         join restaurants r on r.id = $3;
